2022 PH Election - Marikina City

(1/2) Aside from BBM's 7-point win over Isko in Manila, the closest election in the Metro was in Marikina. BBM only beat Leni here by about 10%. 

9 out of 16 brgys in the city were decided with a <10% win margin.

#Halalan2022 #Eleksyon2022 https://t.co/JmdplXHtqi

2022 Philippine VP Election - Marikina City

Sara Duterte won Marikina with 48.5% of the vote.

Kiko got 27.6% and won 1 brgy (Concepcion Dos) compared to Leni's 5. 

Sotto almost got 2nd place in Brgy Malanday.
